<div class="topstuff">
  <h2>How to help</h2>
  </div>
  <div class = "textstuff">
    <p>If you know anyone that might be in danger of being abused, there are ways you can help. Report the situation as soon as possible to the authorities. Please keep in mind if you are putting the child in danger when trying to help. Communicate with the child clearly about the situation.</P>
  <h3>here are some resources for at risk children</h3>
  <ul>
    <a href="https://www.cys-la.org/mediators-c1s45"> <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/dca2de_0ee8520681964ab9846826e5e6fdcedb~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_176,h_176,al_c,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/dca2de_0ee8520681964ab9846826e5e6fdcedb~mv2.png" alt="picture of cys logo"/> </a>
    
  
  
  
  <h4>when communicating with the child keep in mind:</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Offer a drink or snack to make them comfortable</li>
    <li>validate them and tell them you believe them</li>
    <li>provide toys and child friendly enviroment</li>
    <li>be patient with them if they do not wish to talk</li>
    <li>understand what the child wants from you</li>
    <li>use terminology the child will understand</li>
    <li>stay kind, calm, and collected</li>
  </div>
